message.body: Guess where Alec and I are going right now? Rusty nail. Did you go there in high school!?
It's a bar that we go to for reunions
I've been there to watch some friends play but not in high school.
That's Awesome!! Please give Ish a big hug & tell him Happy Thanksgiving from the O'Malley Clan!!
We used to mostly go to the Great American Pub in Narberth. We grew up a couple blocks from there. I miss that. I used to love going out the night before Thanksgiving.
